Title: Object: Enfin moi qui vous parle...si je vous disais que j'ai vu, de mes propres yeux...
Series: Sixième Album lithographique
Description: Numbered 6: Two soldiers seated at a table outside a building; the soldier at right relates stories of his adventures in Egypt, holding a bottle in his hand; the other soldier listens, engrossed, leaning on his elbow; both have bags on their backs; beyond at right, a soldier in the doorway, and at left, two soldiers seen from behind; taken from an album published in 1826. 1826 Lithograph
Bibliographic references: IFF / Inventaire du Fonds Français: Bibliothèque Nationale, Département des Estampes (44)
Adeline 1880 / Hippolyte Bellangé et son oeuvre (53)
Beraldi 1885-92 / Les Graveurs du dix-neuvième siècle (4)
